        Who We Are

    



            Who We Are

        













Making your day better—in small but meaningful ways.
We see big potential in life’s little moments. Brushing teeth. Washing hair. Showering. Shaving. Caring for the baby. Cleaning the house. Doing the dishes, and the laundry. We make the products that help make these moments a little easier.




I need to…

View P&G's Privacy Policy
divider

View History of Innovation
divider

View Core Strengths













Our Approach



    We work hard every day to make quality products and services that improve people’s lives, now and for generations to come. 















Leadership Team



    People make the difference at P&G. That’s why we develop leaders from every region and every level of the company.















Leadership Letters



    At P&G, we aspire to help build a better world, inside and outside of our company. Read what our leaders say about how we strive to achieve these goals every day throughout P&G.















Structure & Governance



    We believe global growth brings a high responsibility to invest in the communities where we live and work.















Policies & Practices



    Doing the right thing is the foundation of who we are—from the products we make to the policies that guide the way we do business. 















Heritage



    From our humble beginnings in 1837, P&G has built a rich heritage of touching lives with brands that make everyday life a little better.















External Recognition



    We are consistently recognized as a leading global company, earning a variety of awards and recognition in several key areas.















