        Sustainability

    



            Sustainability

        













Helping to Enable Consumers to Make More Sustainable Choices
P&G is committed to offering consumers brands that meet and exceed expectations without compromise. We have established a long-term vision and set short-term goals to ensure we stay on track to one day achieve that vision. 




I need to…

View P&G’s Citizenship Report
divider

View Our Objective
divider

View what we're focused on













At a Glance



    Sustainable thinking is present in everything we do. Learn more about our efforts and strategy toward a sustainable future.















Environmental Sustainability



    We work each day to create innovative and sustainable products that people love, without trade-offs in price or performance.















Community Impact



    It is part of our culture to give back to the  communities where we live and work.















Latest Sustainability Stories



    Check out what we are doing to reduce our environmental footprint in our focus areas of climate, water and waste.















